'''公正网'''（{{lang-en|Justia}}），[[意译|意译]]也作'''正义网'''，[[音译|音译]]作'''贾斯蒂亚'''，是一家位于[[美国|美国]][[加利福尼亚州|加利福尼亚州]][[芒廷维尤_(加利福尼亚州)|山景城]]的专业从事[[法律|法律]][[信息|信息]][[检索|检索]]的[[网站|网站]]，于2003年创立。創立者是[[提姆·斯坦利|提姆·斯坦利]]（Tim Stanley）和[[史黛西·斯特恩|史黛西·斯特恩]]（Stacy Stern）两位[[律师|律师]]<ref>Nicole Black.{{cite news|url=https://www.abajournal.com/web/article/lawyers-have-many-options-when-it-comes-to-designing-their-firms-websites|title=Lawyers have many options when it comes to designing their firm's websites|date=2019-09-24|website=ABA Journal|accessdate=2020-07-10|archive-date=2020-10-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201026131214/https://www.abajournal.com/web/article/lawyers-have-many-options-when-it-comes-to-designing-their-firms-websites|dead-url=no}}</ref>。它是世界上最大的[[在线|在线]][[法律|法律]][[案例|案例]][[数据库|数据库]]之一。该网站免费提供[[判例法|判例法]]（case law）、[[法典|法典]]、意见摘要和其它基本法律[[文本|文本]]，并为其律师名录和网络托管提供付费服务<ref>{{cite news |last=Carter |first=Terry |date=2017-04-12 |title=Justia's Stacy Stern finds real profit in making things free |url=http://www.abajournal.com/legalrebels/article/rebels_podcast_episode_015 |work=ABA Journal |accessdate= |archive-date=2020-08-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200810190439/https://www.abajournal.com/legalrebels/article/rebels_podcast_episode_015 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。"Justia"一词是[[拉丁语|拉丁语]]，意为“（主要指人）公平（equality<ref name="千华数位文化舒怀2019">{{cite book|author1=千华数位文化|author2=舒怀|title=109年名师压箱秘籍-教育行政学精析[高普考╱地方特考]|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=FFK-DwAAQBAJ&pg=PA390|date=2019-11-15|publisher=千华数位文化|isbn=978-986-487-879-6|pages=390–|access-date=2020-07-10|archive-date=2020-09-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200914144031/https://books.google.com/books?id=FFK-DwAAQBAJ&pg=PA390|dead-url=no}}</ref>）、公正（fair<ref>{{cite book|title=艾蜜莉的谜语|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=2eA0DwAAQBAJ&pg=PA70|date=2016-10-26|publisher=费思经典|isbn=978-957-43-3095-9|pages=70–|access-date=2020-07-10|archive-date=2020-07-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200710102839/https://books.google.com/books?id=2eA0DwAAQBAJ&pg=PA70|dead-url=no}}</ref>）、正义（Justice<ref name="熊逸2019">{{cite book|author=熊逸|title=正义从哪里来|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=vTvgDwAAQBAJ&pg=PT26|date=2019-04-01|publisher=|isbn=978-7-5139-2267-8|pages=26–|access-date=2020-07-10|archive-date=2020-07-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200718053810/https://books.google.com/books?id=vTvgDwAAQBAJ&pg=PT26|dead-url=no}}</ref>）”以及“合适的或者正确的东西”<ref name="Reisch2014">{{cite book|author=Michael Reisch|title=Routledge International Handbook of Social Justice|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=STVEAwAAQBAJ&pg=PA216|date=2014-04-03|publisher=Routledge|isbn=978-1-317-93401-1|pages=216–|access-date=2020-07-10|archive-date=2020-08-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200803211011/https://books.google.com/books?id=STVEAwAAQBAJ&pg=PA216|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2007年，《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》称，公正网每月花费约“一万[[美元|美元]]”以“复制”[[美国最高法院|美国最高法院]]的文件并在线发布，使公众无需付费即可获得它們<ref>{{cite news |last=Markoff |first=John |date=2007-08-20 |title=A Quest to Get More Court Rulings Online, and Free |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2007/08/20/technology/20westlaw.html |work=[[The_New_York_Times|The New York Times]] |7= |accessdate=2020-07-10 |archive-date=2020-11-24 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201124092615/https://www.nytimes.com/2007/08/20/technology/20westlaw.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

